{"tid":2338643,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"黑警：會部署足夠警力防止平安夜有非法集結","createTime":"2020-12-24T06:46:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-24T07:12:04.000Z","uid":20933,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"a2274707df65ef57462abe2be2956417afd03092","tid":2338643,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T06:46:46.000Z","msg":"警方表示，留意到有人於網上號召其他人，今日在全港各區進行未經批准的集結，警方會在相關地點部署足夠警力，迅速果斷執法，強調絕不容忍任何違法行為。 <br />\n<br />\n警方在社交網站表示，有關活動沒有獲得警方的不反對通知書，亦有可能違反限聚令，強調疫情仍然嚴峻，呼籲市民應做好防疫措施，盡量減少社交活動及避免到人多聚集的地方，亦不要參與任何未經批准集結或受禁的群組聚集。 <br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2372073\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2372073&d=otIFGLHjmDp%2FicXUVK76Mer6kk4zB%2BnGw4DSdwpbM%2Bg%3D&h=482e30d3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2372073</a>"},{"pid":"921be075a3ec9bfd5a6ede9ed4e397571b9fcc82","tid":2338643,"uid":214502,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T06:48:24.000Z","msg":"眼紅人地有女屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da17b1f4f5b8788f72e5001fe4d14572ea8b08d7","tid":2338643,"uid":58630,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T06:50:02.000Z","msg":"好多人會係屋企聚集 點防<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8226e1cf9e3108538c4b68b243374a4f3e3cbab7","tid":2338643,"uid":73565,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T06:51:01.000Z","msg":"今晚約左朋友落老蘭<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1069168fa9f9915e5c346f1c408900515182dbd","tid":2338643,"uid":14941,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T06:52:24.000Z","msg":"今晚又一城有行動"},{"pid":"5dced8400ab4b3d4f4e07408c9307cc1a9bda016","tid":2338643,"uid":187664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T06:53:45.000Z","ms